    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I have <a href=\"http://www.eclipsezone.com/eclipse/forums/t53459.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">this article</a> bookmarked on setting this up for Java 5 and below.</p>\n<p>Basically <a href=\"http://download.oracle.com/otn_hosted_doc/jdeveloper/904preview/jdk14doc/docs/tooldocs/windows/jdb.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">run it with</a>:</p>\n<pre><code>-Xdebug -Xrunjdwp:transport=dt_socket,server=y,suspend=n,address=1044\n</code></pre>\n<p>For <a href=\"http://javahowto.blogspot.ru/2010/09/java-agentlibjdwp-for-attaching.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Java 5 and above</a>, run it with:</p>\n<pre><code>-agentlib:jdwp=transport=dt_socket,server=y,suspend=n,address=1044\n</code></pre>\n<p>If you want Java to <strong>wait for you to connect</strong> before executing the application, replace <code>suspend=n</code> with <code>suspend=y</code>.</p>\n"
  }, {
